space.arim.api.chat

Class Message

  • java.lang.Object
    • space.arim.api.chat.Message

  • public class Message
extends Object
    A sendable message comprised of an array of Component or JsonComponent objects.

    Each Component is considered distinct. No formatting from the first Component affects the next.
    Accordingly, no Format.RESET codes need be applied at the start or end of a Component.
    Author:
    A248
